---
import Section from "./Section.astro"
import ContentItem from "./ContentItem.astro"
import { experience, talks } from "../data/site"
---

<Section id="about" title="About" subtitle="Still falling, still learning.">
  <p class="will-animate delay-100">
    For years, I've worked as a frontend engineer, building interfaces for
    large-scale projects. I've learned precision, structure, and how to make
    complex systems feel simple.
  </p>
  <p class="will-animate delay-200">
    But somewhere along the way, I started craving something more personal —
    something that could reflect not just what I do, but why I do it.
  </p>
  <p class="will-animate delay-300">
    This site is where that idea starts to take form.
  </p>
  <p class="will-animate delay-400">
    It's not a portfolio in the traditional sense. It's a living space — a place
    to experiment, to connect dots between design and engineering, to explore
    the balance between logic and emotion.
  </p>
  <p class="will-animate delay-500">
    I'm learning to move slower. To build with intention. To make things that
    last.
  </p>
  <p class="will-animate delay-500">
    This space will grow with me — changing shape as I do.
  </p>

  <div class="will-animate">
    <h3
      class="mb-6 font-serif text-[14px] font-medium tracking-wide text-stone-500 uppercase dark:text-stone-400"
    >
      Experience
    </h3>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      {
        experience.map((item) => (
          <ContentItem
            title={item.role}
            subtitle={item.company}
            period={item.period}
            description={item.description}
          />
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="will-animate border-t border-stone-200 pt-8 dark:border-stone-700"
  >
    <h3
      class="mb-6 font-serif text-[14px] font-medium tracking-wide text-stone-500 uppercase dark:text-stone-400"
    >
      Talks & Writings
    </h3>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      {
        talks.map((item) => (
          <ContentItem
            title={item.title}
            subtitle={item.type}
            period={item.year}
            description={item.description}
            href={item.href}
          />
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
